{"tid":1684602,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今晚太子悼念將會出現琴晚屯門圍狗屋劇本","createTime":"2019-10-31T07:33:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-31T09:12:46.000Z","uid":12354,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"737bffad513089b2cb58c59b452f68e0c132630e","tid":1684602,"uid":12354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T07:33:05.000Z","msg":"同樣地係預早時間比PoPo準備<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同樣地係圍狗屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(太子悼念完會唔會圍狗圍大家心知肚明啦 <br />\n831到今日出現過唔知幾多次）<br />\n<br />\n同樣地黑警已經知道手足會點走 識得Set包圍網<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唯一唔肯定嘅係會唔會有藍絲出嚟挑機拖時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山 各有各做<br />\n出唔出大家自己考慮<br />\n出嘅話緊記一樣野<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">流動性</span><br />\n任何地方唔好停留超過5分鐘<br />\n冇目標地留喺同一個位係冇用的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f35108f326277007bab22e03ab13697faaa5b5a0","tid":1684602,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T07:36:35.000Z","msg":"【拒絕送頭】建議和理非合法哀悼太子831死者方法<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1684561\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1684561</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"86a527b145cbc6945869b02cd9570e9cc01b830a","tid":1684602,"uid":3358,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T07:44:40.000Z","msg":"悼念完即散係最好<br />\n圍狗屋無任何作用"},{"pid":"6db78fe6b5a93195caaf9006b8277116a825ef7a","tid":1684602,"uid":280475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T07:45:31.000Z","msg":"Tui"},{"pid":"a8c54312f909e00fc4f825770fb872067aec9af4","tid":1684602,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T07:50:14.000Z","msg":"大興含洞J地根本係地形殺"},{"pid":"20ff5170cba789c01c756e8e1fe156b6319d406a","tid":1684602,"uid":12354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"rep